snippet.title: Powerglove reloaded trailer
snippet.description: Trailer of the Amiga game Powerglove reloaded. The game is available for Amiga (A500 with 1 MB or better), Windows, Mac and Linux. More infos at http://www.lazycow.de/powerglove
